data.description: Assumable VA loan with a 2.9% interest rate for eligible buyers. Discover this beautifully updated 3-bedroom, 1.5-bath gem nestled in the heart of Cleveland. This charming home boasts modern amenities while preserving its classic character. Bright and airy living spaces welcome you, featuring tasteful finishes and ample natural light. The spacious kitchen is a culinary dream, complete with sleek countertops and contemporary appliances. Three well-appointed bedrooms offer comfort and privacy, while the updated bathrooms exude a spa-like ambiance. Outside, a lush backyard provides a tranquil retreat, perfect for relaxation or entertaining. Located in a desirable neighborhood, this residence offers both convenience and style, making it the perfect place to call home in Cleveland. Updates: Roof (2021) and HVAC (2021).
